dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Kevin Long. May I have your name, please?
Hi Kevin, my name is Debra Brown.
Great to meet you, Debra. Could you please provide me with your policy number?
Sure, it's zero two three four five six.
Thank you, Debra. Next, could you confirm your date of birth?
My date of birth is January twenty-third, nineteen eighty-five.
Thank you for confirming, Debra. Is there anything specific you'd like to inquire about today?
I wanted to check the status of my recent claim.
I can assist you with that. Let me check the system. Thank you for your patience, Debra.
I have checked the status of your claim. Everything is processing smoothly. Do you have any other questions for me today?
No, that's all. Thank you, Kevin, for your help.
You're welcome, Debra. If you need any further assistance, don't hesitate to contact us. Have a great day!
